</li>
<li><p>版本切換</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo update-java-alternatives <span class="operator">-s</span> java-<span class="number">8</span>-oracle</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
