    <updated>2015-05-23T03:20:08.804Z</updated>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="安裝Activator">安裝Activator</h2><p>先下載<a href="http://www.typesafe.com/community/core-tools/activator-and-sbt" target="_blank" rel="external">Activator</a><br>解壓到<code>D:\Program Files\activator-1.3.2</code><br>將<code>D:\Program Files\activator-1.3.2</code>加到環境變量Path中<br>在你的項目目錄中執行以下命令，驗證是否安裝成功</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">activator -help</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="創建Play項目">創建Play項目</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">activator new demo play-java</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> demo</span><br><span class="line">activator</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="安裝Eclipse插件">安裝Eclipse插件</h2><p><a href="http://scala-ide.org/download/current.html" target="_blank" rel="external">Scala IDE</a><br>在Eclipse中Install New Software增加宰割Update Site，記得安裝Play Support</p>
<h2 id="創建Eclipse項目">創建Eclipse項目</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">eclipse with-source=<span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="跑起來看看">跑起來看看</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">run</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>在瀏覽器中打開<a href="http://localhost:9000" target="_blank" rel="external">http://localhost:9000</a>，項目就跑起來了╰(￣▽￣)╮</p>
]]></content>
